WindwardRestApi.Model

Class Template

  • java.lang.Object
    • WindwardRestApi.Model.Template

  • public class Template
extends java.lang.Object
    Template. This is what is sent to the server to make a request.
    This makes use of @JacksonXmlProperty for all properties because they must be correctly capitalized in a request (in a response we ignore capitalization).
